                     <td><span class="ItemHeading">Mind the Gap</span><span class="ItemType"> [<a href="http://www.earthdawn-classic.com/projects/selectProject.html;jsessionid=aE3hQ88W5MZc?id=152144">Web Site Announcements</a>]</span><br><div class="ItemInfo">Posted on 
                           April 26, 2006 7:43 PM
