                  <tr>
                     <td valign="top" class="TableCell">
                        <img align="right" src="http://www.ardanyan.de/RBL700.thumb.jpg" alt="" />The <strong>Shards</strong> series is a collection
                        of adventures and encounters for the <strong>Earthdawn</strong> game. Intended as an inexpensive adventure resource      
                        for <strong>Earthdawn</strong> gamemasters, and -like the recent <strong>Name-giver&rsquo;s Compendium                   
                        Open Call</strong> - a springboard for aspiring writers. The <strong>Shards</strong> series will be published            
                        online via <a href="http://www.drivethrurpg.com">DriveThruRPG.com</a>, and might even see print at a                     
                        later stage (possibly as a collection once the series has produced a suitable number of issues). Here&rsquo;s a direct   
                        link to the <a href="http://www.earthdawn-classic.com/cms/shardssubmissionguidelines.html">submission guidelines</a>,    
                        which can also be found in our <strong>Articles</strong> section. If you have written an adventure that isn&rsquo;t      
                        big enough for a full-blown adventure book, this is the place to go. <br /><br /><strong>Shards Volume I:                
                        Journey to Lang</strong> is available now (<a href="http://www.drivethrurpg.com/catalog/product_info.php?cPath=205_236&amp;products_id=3742">click
                        here</a>). Please use our <strong>Shards</strong> forum if you                            have any questions             
                        regarding this series.<br />
                        
                     </td>
                  </tr>
