                  <tr>
                     <td valign="top" class="TableCellAlternate">
                        Looks like the <b>Name-givers' Compendium</b> will be a very pretty book - we put far more work into it than originally intended,
                        but the sheer amount of new material is really worth the effort. The 'minor Disciplines' have grown up.<p/>While the development
                        phase on the <b>Name-giver's Compendium</b> is still in full swing, we've finally reached a point where we were able to determine
                        which of the submissions are in and which are out. The decisions haven't been easy, as the material was pretty good overall.
                        <p/>All participants of the Open Call have been notified on the status of their submissions - our congratulations to everyone
                        and thanks a lot for your work! Very soon, there will be more chances for you to submit material, and we would be glad to
                        see more proposals--watch this space for an announcement on the <b>Shards</b> series.
                        
                     </td>
                  </tr>
