                     <td valign="top" class="TableCell">
                        (From DriveThruRPG) Yes, it's that time once again. From Saturday (March 4th) until Monday (March 6th) we will be offering
                        a 20% off coupon that you can use for nearly every product on the site. Just enter the code <b>gmday</b> (all lowercase) during
                        checkout, and this coupon will be applied to your order.<p/>You can use this coupon as many times as you want, on as many
                        books as you want. So if you've been trying to decide whether or not to get a certain eBook, now is the time!
                        
