                  <tr>
                     <td valign="top" class="TableCellAlternate">
                        Our Open Call for Writers regarding the forthcoming <b>Name-givers Compendium</b> is now closed, further submissions will
                        not be accepted. A big <b>THANK YOU</b> to everyone who participated, we have received more material than expected and almost
                        all of it is really good, too.<p/>We will now evaluate the entries to find the best combination for the <b>Name-givers Compendium</b>,
                        and announce the winners when the time is due. <i>Every</i> participant will receive an eMail on the status of his submissions,
                        although this may take a while since we have to make a few hard choices.<p/>Some statistics on this open call: <br/><li/><b>Total
                        number of entries:</b> 42<br/><li/><b>Most popular Discipline:</b> Horror Stalker (closely followed by the Boatman and the
                        Traveled Scholar)<br/><li/><b>Highest Number of entries by a single writer:</b> 10<br/><br/>
                        
                     </td>
                  </tr>
