                     <td valign="top" class="TableCell">
                        <img src="http://www.redbrick.co.nz/RBL506.thumb.jpg" align="right" /><br/>While the release of <b>Ardanyan's Revenge</b>
                        is a little delayed due to to the Battlecry convention this weekend, we are going to sweeten the wait and give you another
                        free PDF. <b>Rites of Protection and Passage</b> provides general information on how kaers were designed and built before
                        the Scourge. Gamemasters will find useful hints on how to set up and run a kaer campaign and what considerations to make when
                        designing kaers and kaer-dweller characters. <p/>Look for it in the <a href="http://www.earthdawn-classic.com/downloads/viewDownloads.html?id=2442">Downloads,
                        Free Stuff</a> folder!
                        
